Computer             !=         storage
  ^                                ^
  | (capacity for logic)           | (capacity for data)
  V                                V
Logic               !=             data (database native binary or varaible width plaintext)

Supplemental resources
Memory
Cooling
PCB (logistics and allocations)
PSU

Worst type of vendor lock in. Decoupling: Separate your data from your configuration, and your configuration from the tools that apply it.
